You can find the following folders:

1) SIR__course_BRC2.pptx with the actual presentation
   At the end of the presentation you can find the statements of 10 exercises

2) the folder SIR_exercises, whith 10 subfolder containing the different
exercises.
   In each subfolder (exercise1, exercise2 ... etc) you can find the data
   to solve the exercise and the subfolder "solution" in which you can find
   a Readme file explaining the solution.


